Vivint Values Your Privacy
Vivint’s commitment to providing security and peace of mind extends to how we handle Personal Information. Vivint builds and maintains consumer trust by protecting Personal Information including Sensitive Personal Information.
Information We Collect
The Personal Information we collect depends on the types of products and services you use. We use and process the Personal Information we collect for the purposes outlined in the
How We Use Your Information
section below.
